{
  "stem": "11611.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But with a very nebulous, unstated charge.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because what he was really charged with was fronting for a group that was charged with undermining the German economy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I can tell you, these people wanted to undermine the German economy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The German economy was an economy they knew very well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had functioned as slave laborers for four years for it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This guy was actually used.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He didn't know what the hell he was doing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He didn't make any money, or anything else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was used by a bunch of young-- young kids from the DP camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the first thing we did was we raised a couple bucks here and there around the court house from the staff that was left.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We applied to get him out on bail, and we were successful, surprisingly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who was the judge?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some lawyer from California, working for the occupation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So as soon as we got him out of jail, I told him, the first thing you do is get your rear end to Switzerland and stay there-- which he could do.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the trial then went on, on a breach of bail-- and they confiscated the $300 or so that we put up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They tried him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They found him guilty of conduct unbecoming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were no-- no such charge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is a-- an assimilated army charge, conduct unbecoming an officer and gentleman-- which is very nebulous in military law.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they convicted him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They gave him a five-year sentence, which was almost as much as any defendant at the Nuremberg Trials.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Different attitude.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Five years for undermining the German economy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, he never came back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He died in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know what the sentences were.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
